  "class.sensoryabyss.the_blinded": "目盲者",
  "class.sensoryabyss.the_blinded.description": "失去视力的你，如今通过声音感知世界。标记猎物，获取赏金。",
  "class.sensoryabyss.the_deafened": "失聪者",
  "class.sensoryabyss.the_deafened.description": "对世间之声充耳不闻，却能感受大地的每次震颤。旅途赋予你感知震动的能力。",
  "class.sensoryabyss.the_numb": "麻木者",
  "class.sensoryabyss.the_numb.description": "痛苦已成记忆。剩下的是一副拒绝停歇的躯体——直到代价来临。",
  "class.sensoryabyss.the_anosmiac": "失嗅者",
  "class.sensoryabyss.the_anosmiac.description": "腐败不再侵袭你。毒害他人的，只会滋养取而代之的饥渴。",
  "class.sensoryabyss.the_unfed": "无食者",
  "class.sensoryabyss.the_unfed.description": "食物味同嚼蜡。你必须汲取生灵精华才能生存，并获取他们的力量。",
  "_comment_subclasses": "子职业",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.radiant": "光耀者",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.shade": "暗影",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.frequency_rider": "声频骑士",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.harmonic": "谐律者",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.bloodhound": "寻血猎手",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.miasma_walker": "瘴气行者",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.monolith": "巨像",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.shardborn": "碎片之子",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.corpse_eater": "顶尖掠食者",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.necromancer": "死亡统帅",
  "_comment_subclass_descriptions": "子职业描述",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.radiant.description": "华丽的范围压制。将光化作武器——超载回声脉冲与新星爆发。",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.shade.description": "冷静而精准。在黑暗中成长——暗影突刺目标，制造黑暗区域潜行。",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.frequency_rider.description": "动能射手。回声射击在敌人间弹射；共振突进穿梭战场。战斗累积频率层数，提升移速、射速与伤害。",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.harmonic.description": "支援谐律。切换歌曲光环强化盟友，根据承受伤害累积渐强能量，连锁锥形波-脉冲-波动触发终曲。",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.monolith.description": "活体堡垒。吸收材料并化为己用——石甲、铁骨、熔岩护盾。",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.shardborn.description": "行走的兵器。吸收材料并将其武器化——锯齿锋刃、穿刺打击、爆发喷涌。",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.corpse_eater.description": "操纵血液在三种战斗姿态间切换——打击者、掠夺者、饮血者。解读战局，引导血液，发动近战处决。",
  "subclass.sensoryabyss.necromancer.description": "指挥亡灵大军。灵魂为复活之资；姿态号令死者。你的军队即是盾牌。",
  "_comment_abilities": "能力",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.echo_vision": "回声视界",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.echo_vision.description": "永久声呐。虽盲，却借回声感知世界。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.luminance_absorption": "光暗吸收",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.luminance_absorption.description": "躯体适应光照。亮处充盈光能条，暗处充盈暗影条。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.searing_pulse": "灼热脉冲",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.searing_pulse.description": "回声脉冲，伤害所有侦测到的实体。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.nova": "新星",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.nova.description": "大规模闪光爆发。对范围内所有敌人造成巨额伤害和致盲。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.shadow_strike": "暗影突刺",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.shadow_strike.description": "冲向一个检测到的回声标记，造成巨额单体伤害。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.blackout": "黑暗降临",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.blackout.description": "制造黑暗区域。区域内获得潜行与强化回声视觉。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.sound_drain": "声音汲取",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.sound_drain.description": "长按汲取附近生物的声音。充盈共振，进化技能。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.shockwave_cone": "冲击锥",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.shockwave_cone.description": "释放锥形音波。造成伤害与击退。随‘侵略’之音进化。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.sonic_pulse": "声呐脉冲",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.sonic_pulse.description": "探测脉冲，穿透墙壁揭示所有实体。随‘掠食’之音进化。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.ground_slam": "地面猛击",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.ground_slam.description": "蓄力猛击地面。范围伤害并留下残留区域。随‘击打’之音进化。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.harmonic_wave": "和谐音波",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.harmonic_wave.description": "向外发出治愈波。治疗盟友，净化负面效果。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.resonance_burst": "共振爆发",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.resonance_burst.description": "释放储存的痛苦尖叫。恐慌技能，造成击退与混乱。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.sound_barrier": "音障",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.sound_barrier.description": "将吸收的哀嚎塑造成防护穹顶。降低盟友收到的伤害，偏转弹射物。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.material_absorb": "材料吸收",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.material_absorb.description": "长按方块将其吸收。根据材料元素与品级获得增益。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.fortify": "坚壁",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.fortify.description": "将吸收的材料化作防御外壳。附带元素主题次要效果。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.encrust": "结壳",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.encrust.description": "向外排出材料，创造物理屏障构造体。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.petrify": "石化",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.petrify.description": "全身转化为吸收的材料。巨额减伤并附带伤害光环。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.material_strike": "材料打击",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.material_strike.description": "将材料导入毁灭性的强化近战攻击，附带元素效果。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.shrapnel_burst": "碎片迸射",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.shrapnel_burst.description": "向四面八方排出材料碎片。范围爆发，附带元素减益。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.cataclysm": "灾变",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.cataclysm.description": "大规模材料引爆。爆炸加残留危险区域。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.toxic_empowerment": "毒性强化",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.toxic_empowerment.description": "受到负面效果时获得力量。反复接触获得免疫。",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.universal_essence": "万能精华",
  "ability.sensoryabyss.universal_essence.description": "吸收击杀生物的精华。获得其属性与能力。",
